cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use Delta, cite the software release described by this file."
type: software
title: "Delta: An Uncertainty-Aware Stylometry Workbench"
abstract: >-
  Delta is a scholar-led, no-code workbench for literary stylometry. It is
  designed to expose corpus checks, parameter sensitivity, interpretive limits,
  and FAIR-oriented run evidence alongside supported analyses.
version: 0.0.0.dev0
authors:
